{
  "info": {
    "name": "CyberLearnix — Payment APIs",
    "_postman_id": "cyberlearnix-payment-apis-v1",
    "description": "All payment-related APIs for CyberLearnix LMS.\n\n**Services covered:**\n- Enrollment Service (port 8083) — PayU payment flow + coupons\n- Form Service (port 8087) — Form-linked payment flow\n- Admin Service (port 8092) — Order management\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Set `authToken` variable to a valid JWT (obtained from login)\n2. Set `formResponseId` to a real form response ID\n3. Set `formId` to a real form ID\n\n**PayU Test Credentials (from .env):**\n- Merchant Key: `XidEdD`\n- Salt: `4JPMTxOzkJMchiHLrdFcSgkcXTuzx1Bd`\n- Test URL: https://test.payu.in/_payment",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl_enrollment", "value": "http://localhost:8083", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "baseUrl_form",       "value": "http://localhost:8087", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "baseUrl_admin",      "value": "http://localhost:8092", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "authToken",          "value": "PASTE_JWT_HERE",        "type": "string" },
    { "key": "txnid",              "value": "TXN-ABCDEF1234567890",  "type": "string" },
    { "key": "formResponseId",     "value": "1",                     "type": "string" },
    { "key": "formId",             "value": "your-form-id",          "type": "string" },
    { "key": "couponId",           "value": "1",                     "type": "string" },
    { "key": "orderId",            "value": "1",                     "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [

    {
      "name": "1. Enrollment Service — PayU Payment Flow",
      "description": "Full PayU payment flow through enrollment-service (port 8083).\n\nFlow: initiate → PayU form submit → callback/webhook → status poll",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "1.1 Initiate Payment",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/payments/initiate",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "payments", "initiate"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"formResponseId\": {{formResponseId}},\n  \"studentName\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"studentEmail\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"studentPhone\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"couponCode\": \"\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Step 1 of the PayU flow. Returns PayU form fields + signed hash.\n\n**Response contains:**\n- `payuUrl` — PayU endpoint to submit to (https://secure.payu.in/_payment)\n- `txnid` — transaction ID (save for status polling)\n- `key`, `hash`, `amount`, `productinfo`, `firstname`, `email`, `phone`, `surl`, `furl`\n\nAfter getting this response, the frontend submits a form POST to PayU's URL with these fields."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "1.2 Initiate Payment (with Coupon)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/payments/initiate",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "payments", "initiate"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"formResponseId\": {{formResponseId}},\n  \"studentName\": \"Jane Doe\",\n  \"studentEmail\": \"jane@example.com\",\n  \"studentPhone\": \"9876543210\",\n  \"couponCode\": \"SAVE10\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Same as initiate but applies a coupon code. Discount is deducted from the final amount sent to PayU."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "1.3 Simulate PayU Success Callback",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/payments/callback/success?txnid={{txnid}}&mihpayid=403993715522&mode=CC&status=success&amount=5000.00&productinfo=Python+Bootcamp&firstname=John+Doe&email=john%40example.com&phone=9876543210&hash=REPLACE_WITH_VALID_HASH&bank_ref_num=1234567890",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "payments", "callback", "success"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "txnid",       "value": "{{txnid}}" },
                { "key": "mihpayid",    "value": "403993715522" },
                { "key": "mode",        "value": "CC" },
                { "key": "status",      "value": "success" },
                { "key": "amount",      "value": "5000.00" },
                { "key": "productinfo", "value": "Python Bootcamp" },
                { "key": "firstname",   "value": "John Doe" },
                { "key": "email",       "value": "john@example.com" },
                { "key": "phone",       "value": "9876543210" },
                { "key": "hash",        "value": "REPLACE_WITH_VALID_HASH" },
                { "key": "bank_ref_num","value": "1234567890" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "PayU browser-redirects the student here after a SUCCESSFUL payment.\n\n⚠️ In production this is called by PayU's browser redirect — not directly by you.\n\nFor testing: replace `hash` with a correctly computed SHA-512 hash.\n\nHash format (reverse hash): `SALT|status|udf5|udf4|udf3|udf2|udf1|email|firstname|productinfo|amount|txnid|key`\n\nThis endpoint verifies the hash, marks the transaction as PAID, and redirects to the frontend."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "1.4 Simulate PayU Failure Callback",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/payments/callback/failure?txnid={{txnid}}&mihpayid=&mode=&status=failure&amount=5000.00&productinfo=Python+Bootcamp&firstname=John+Doe&email=john%40example.com&error_Message=Payment+declined&hash=REPLACE_WITH_VALID_HASH",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "payments", "callback", "failure"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "txnid",         "value": "{{txnid}}" },
                { "key": "mihpayid",      "value": "" },
                { "key": "mode",          "value": "" },
                { "key": "status",        "value": "failure" },
                { "key": "amount",        "value": "5000.00" },
                { "key": "productinfo",   "value": "Python Bootcamp" },
                { "key": "firstname",     "value": "John Doe" },
                { "key": "email",         "value": "john@example.com" },
                { "key": "error_Message", "value": "Payment declined" },
                { "key": "hash",          "value": "REPLACE_WITH_VALID_HASH" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "PayU browser-redirects here after a FAILED or CANCELLED payment.\n\nMarks the transaction as FAILED and redirects to the frontend with an error status."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "1.5 PayU Server Webhook",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/payments/webhook?txnid={{txnid}}&mihpayid=403993715522&mode=CC&status=success&amount=5000.00&productinfo=Python+Bootcamp&firstname=John+Doe&email=john%40example.com&bank_ref_num=1234567890&hash=REPLACE_WITH_VALID_HASH",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "payments", "webhook"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "txnid",       "value": "{{txnid}}" },
                { "key": "mihpayid",    "value": "403993715522" },
                { "key": "mode",        "value": "CC" },
                { "key": "status",      "value": "success" },
                { "key": "amount",      "value": "5000.00" },
                { "key": "productinfo", "value": "Python Bootcamp" },
                { "key": "firstname",   "value": "John Doe" },
                { "key": "email",       "value": "john@example.com" },
                { "key": "bank_ref_num","value": "1234567890" },
                { "key": "hash",        "value": "REPLACE_WITH_VALID_HASH" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Server-to-server webhook called directly by PayU (not via browser).\n\nAlways returns 200 OK (even on errors) to prevent PayU from retrying.\n\nIdempotent — safe to receive multiple times for the same transaction.\n\nHash format (webhook reverse hash): `SALT|status|udf5|udf4|udf3|udf2|udf1|email|firstname|productinfo|amount|txnid|key`"
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "1.6 Get Payment Status by TxnID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/payments/status/{{txnid}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "payments", "status", "{{txnid}}"]
            },
            "description": "Poll payment status by transaction ID.\n\nReturns full transaction details including: status, amount, mihpayid, mode, bankRefNum, hashVerified, timestamps."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "1.7 Get Payment Status by Form Response ID",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/payments/status/response/{{formResponseId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "payments", "status", "response", "{{formResponseId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Poll payment status by form response ID. Useful when you have the response ID but not the txnid."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "1.8 List Transactions by Form ID (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/payments/form/{{formId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "payments", "form", "{{formId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Admin-only endpoint. Lists all PaymentTransaction records for a given form.\n\nRequires ADMIN role in JWT."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "1.9 Initiate Payment (Legacy — Deprecated)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/payments/payu-payment",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "payments", "payu-payment"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"formResponseId\": {{formResponseId}},\n  \"studentName\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"studentEmail\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"studentPhone\": \"9876543210\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "⚠️ DEPRECATED — kept for backward compatibility. Use `/initiate` instead.\n\nBehaves identically to POST /api/enrollments/payments/initiate."
          },
          "response": []
        }

      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "2. Enrollment Service — Coupons",
      "description": "Coupon/discount management for enrollment payments.\n\nAdmin endpoints require ADMIN role in JWT.\nValidate endpoint is public (no auth needed).",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "2.1 Create Coupon (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/coupons",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "coupons"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"SAVE10\",\n  \"description\": \"10% off on all courses\",\n  \"discountType\": \"PERCENTAGE\",\n  \"discountValue\": 10,\n  \"maxUsages\": 100,\n  \"expiresAt\": \"2026-12-31T23:59:59\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Create a new coupon.\n\n**discountType:** `PERCENTAGE` or `FLAT`\n\nExamples:\n- `PERCENTAGE` + `discountValue: 10` → 10% off\n- `FLAT` + `discountValue: 500` → ₹500 off\n\n`maxUsages` and `expiresAt` are optional."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "2.2 Create Flat Discount Coupon (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/coupons",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "coupons"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"FLAT500\",\n  \"description\": \"₹500 flat discount\",\n  \"discountType\": \"FLAT\",\n  \"discountValue\": 500,\n  \"maxUsages\": 50\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Creates a flat (fixed amount) discount coupon."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "2.3 List All Coupons (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/coupons",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "coupons"]
            },
            "description": "Returns all coupons (active and inactive).\n\nRequires ADMIN role."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "2.4 Deactivate Coupon (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/coupons/{{couponId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "coupons", "{{couponId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Deactivates a coupon by ID. Does not delete — sets `active = false`.\n\nRequires ADMIN role."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "2.5 Validate Coupon (Public)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_enrollment}}/api/enrollments/coupons/validate",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_enrollment}}"],
              "path": ["api", "enrollments", "coupons", "validate"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"code\": \"SAVE10\",\n  \"orderTotal\": 5000\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Public endpoint — no auth required. Validates a coupon code and returns the discount amount.\n\n**Response:**\n- `valid`: boolean\n- `discountAmount`: calculated discount in ₹\n- `finalAmount`: order total after discount\n- `message`: human-readable result"
          },
          "response": []
        }

      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "3. Form Service — Payment Flow",
      "description": "Payment flow for form-linked enrollments via form-service (port 8087).\n\nSimilar to enrollment-service payment flow but tied to form submissions.",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "3.1 Initiate Form Payment",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_form}}/api/forms/payments/initiate",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_form}}"],
              "path": ["api", "forms", "payments", "initiate"]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"formResponseId\": {{formResponseId}},\n  \"studentName\": \"John Doe\",\n  \"studentEmail\": \"john@example.com\",\n  \"studentPhone\": \"9876543210\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "description": "Initiates payment for a form response.\n\nReturns PayU form fields + hash for browser-side form submission to PayU."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "3.2 Simulate PayU Success Callback",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_form}}/api/forms/payments/callback/success?txnid={{txnid}}&mihpayid=403993715522&mode=UPI&status=success&amount=2999.00&productinfo=Web+Development+Course&firstname=John+Doe&email=john%40example.com&hash=REPLACE_WITH_VALID_HASH",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_form}}"],
              "path": ["api", "forms", "payments", "callback", "success"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "txnid",       "value": "{{txnid}}" },
                { "key": "mihpayid",    "value": "403993715522" },
                { "key": "mode",        "value": "UPI" },
                { "key": "status",      "value": "success" },
                { "key": "amount",      "value": "2999.00" },
                { "key": "productinfo", "value": "Web Development Course" },
                { "key": "firstname",   "value": "John Doe" },
                { "key": "email",       "value": "john@example.com" },
                { "key": "hash",        "value": "REPLACE_WITH_VALID_HASH" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "PayU browser success redirect for form payments.\n\nVerifies hash and marks form response as PAID."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "3.3 Simulate PayU Failure Callback",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_form}}/api/forms/payments/callback/failure?txnid={{txnid}}&status=failure&amount=2999.00&productinfo=Web+Development+Course&firstname=John+Doe&email=john%40example.com&error_Message=Insufficient+funds&hash=REPLACE_WITH_VALID_HASH",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_form}}"],
              "path": ["api", "forms", "payments", "callback", "failure"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "txnid",         "value": "{{txnid}}" },
                { "key": "status",        "value": "failure" },
                { "key": "amount",        "value": "2999.00" },
                { "key": "productinfo",   "value": "Web Development Course" },
                { "key": "firstname",     "value": "John Doe" },
                { "key": "email",         "value": "john@example.com" },
                { "key": "error_Message", "value": "Insufficient funds" },
                { "key": "hash",          "value": "REPLACE_WITH_VALID_HASH" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "PayU browser failure redirect for form payments.\n\nMarks form response as FAILED."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "3.4 PayU Server Webhook",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_form}}/api/forms/payments/webhook?txnid={{txnid}}&mihpayid=403993715522&mode=NB&status=success&amount=2999.00&productinfo=Web+Development+Course&firstname=John+Doe&email=john%40example.com&bank_ref_num=9876543210&hash=REPLACE_WITH_VALID_HASH",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_form}}"],
              "path": ["api", "forms", "payments", "webhook"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "txnid",       "value": "{{txnid}}" },
                { "key": "mihpayid",    "value": "403993715522" },
                { "key": "mode",        "value": "NB" },
                { "key": "status",      "value": "success" },
                { "key": "amount",      "value": "2999.00" },
                { "key": "productinfo", "value": "Web Development Course" },
                { "key": "firstname",   "value": "John Doe" },
                { "key": "email",       "value": "john@example.com" },
                { "key": "bank_ref_num","value": "9876543210" },
                { "key": "hash",        "value": "REPLACE_WITH_VALID_HASH" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Server-to-server webhook from PayU for form payments.\n\nAlways returns 200. Delegates to handleCallback internally."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "3.5 Get Form Payment Status (Admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_form}}/api/forms/payments/status/{{txnid}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_form}}"],
              "path": ["api", "forms", "payments", "status", "{{txnid}}"]
            },
            "description": "Admin-only. Returns full payment transaction details including student submission data."
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "3.6 Get Form Price Info (Public)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_form}}/api/forms/payments/price/{{formId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_form}}"],
              "path": ["api", "forms", "payments", "price", "{{formId}}"]
            },
            "description": "Public endpoint. Returns payment configuration for a form.\n\n**Response includes:**\n- `paymentEnabled`: boolean\n- `amount`: base price\n- `currency`: e.g. INR\n- `discountEnabled`, `discountType`, `discountValue`\n\nUse this to show the price to the student before payment."
          },
          "response": []
        }

      ]
    },

    {
      "name": "4. Admin Service — Order Management",
      "description": "Admin-only order/payment management endpoints (admin-service, port 8092).\n\nAll endpoints require ADMIN JWT.",
      "item": [

        {
          "name": "4.1 Get All Orders",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_admin}}/api/admin/orders",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_admin}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "orders"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "status", "value": "PAID", "disabled": true, "description": "Filter by status: PENDING, PAID, FAILED, SUCCESS, FAILURE" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Returns all payment transactions/orders.\n\nOptional `status` query param filters results:\n- `PENDING` — initiated but not completed\n- `PAID` / `SUCCESS` — successful payments\n- `FAILED` / `FAILURE` — failed payments"
          },
          "response": []
        },

        {
          "name": "4.2 Get All Orders — Filter by Status",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{authToken}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl_admin}}/api/admin/orders?status=PAID",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl_admin}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "orders"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "status", "value": "PAID" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Filter orders by status. Change `status` to: `PENDING`, `FAILED`, `SUCCESS`."
          },
          "response": []
        },

